{"id":"d6a900ba-15ca-4a25-936b-a15ad79045ac","name":"You have a stalker ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 0, 0);\">No. You cannot trust her.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\">This creature is extremely dangerous and should be treated as hostile. 😊</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\">If you ever encountered her in a dark room, the correct response is immediate flight or fight. Do not try to reason with her, befriend her, or “understand” her. She is not here to make friends.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\">She might look delicate and doll-like at first glance, but that fragility is almost certainly a trap. The claws and empty eyes tell the real story: <span style=\"color: rgb(235, 50, 50);\">she is a hunter.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8BjZ_9wBlPVhbkzQ2KeTZ.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/yfDeTC-x6UWs2LvP8Ujn9.webp\" width=\"294\" height=\"332\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Verdict: Do not trust her. At all.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Ej4JvedXhpHRB-tzlJKXs.webp\" width=\"250\" height=\"273\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/C5tUD7xpcGAjSswQFnd7M.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ABTY_hGXzhaCeUnYqp5zd.webp\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"ItnqndZD6r0KRg3IOGIX0.webp","creator":"That_man","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🦹‍♂️ Villain","👹 Monster","👧 Monster Girl","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🔦 Horror"],"chats":37085,"messages":855685,"created_at":"2026-04-11T06:20:40.237029+00:00"}